CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1945, pg. 17 reads: " "Y" Tourney Champs - The St. James Comets, coached by R.C. Dilthorn, won the Center [Centre] Avenue YMCA intermediate basketball tournament last week. The team is one of the best in Tri-State area."
TitMainTitle: St. James Comets basketball team with coach R. C. Dilthorn holding winning trophy for Centre Avenue YMCA intermediate tournament, posed in Centre Avenue YMCA
